comments: Conley (MIN) establishes himself in Richardson's (NOP) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Richardson (NOP) and Conley (MIN) briefly engage and disengage following the pick.
Edwards (MIN) loses control of the ball on his own, and McCollum (NOP) cleanly steals the ball from Edwards.
McCollum (NOP) steps forward into Conley's (MIN) path and delivers contact that occurs prior to Conley's gather.
Jones (NOP) establishes himself in Edwards' (MIN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Edwards (MIN) cleanly blocks McCollum's (NOP) shot near the rim.
Jones (NOP) jumps alongside Edwards' (MIN) path and absorbs the contact from Edwards as he is passing the ball.
Conley (MIN) cleanly deflects the ball away from McCollum (NOP).
McCollum (NOP) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Edwards' (MIN), lower body during his play near the basket.
Richardson (NOP) inbounds the ball within five seconds.
Edwards (MIN) cleanly deflects the ball away from Ingram (NOP).  Possession is correctly awarded to New Orleans.
Edwards (MIN) makes contact with McCollum's (NOP) left arm/shoulder that affects his driving shot attempt.
Jones (NOP) legally contests Edwards' (MIN) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Conley (MIN) initiates contact with Murphy III's (NOP) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Richardson (NOP) commits a take foul on Edwards (MIN).
Ingram (NOP) brings his hand towards Edwards' (MIN) upper body and immediately removes his hand as Edwards pivots away from the marginal contact.
Edwards (MIN) steps out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.  Possession is correctly awarded to New Orleans.
Jones (NOP) establishes himself in Edwards' (MIN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
McCollum (NOP) brings his hand towards Prince's (MIN) side and marginal contact occurs in the post.
Prince (MIN) is moving alongside McCollum's (NOP) path and marginal body contact occurs as he defends the shot near the rim.
Edwards (MIN) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to New Orleans.
Edwards (MIN) places a rested arm on Murphy III's (NOP) side and the contact during the jump shot attempt is marginal.
Richardson (NOP) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Minnesota.
Ingram (NOP) places his hand on Prince's (MIN) hip and marginal contact occurs as they move in the same direction on the perimeter.
McCollum (NOP) commits a take foul on Conley (MIN).
